name: PERSONAL (NOT FOR RESALE)
description: Any shipment containing used personal articles such as unaccompanied baggage and household goods being shipped for relocation. This is typically used by those who are moving and are having their personal belongings shipped to an international location.

description.EN: Any shipment containing used personal articles such as unaccompanied baggage and household goods being shipped for relocation. This is typically used by those who are moving and are having their personal belongings shipped to an international location.
description.ES: Cualquier envío que contenga artículos personales usados, como equipaje no acompañado y enseres domésticos que se envíen para su reubicación. Por lo general, lo utilizan aquellos que se mudan y sus pertenencias personales se envían a una ubicación internacional.
